# Exercise 4/ Lab 3 - Mutual Exclusion

This project shows an implementation of mutual Exclusion using custom Semaphore class

## Requirements
- Compatible with **Linux** only
- A C++11 compiler
- The MakeFile

## Install
2. Go to Exercises/ directory: cd Exercise Four_Mutual-Exclusion
3. Build project: make CLEAN && make
4. Run: ./mutual_exclusion

## Project/files Content
- **SafeBuffer:** thread safe buffer implementation, require Semaphore class
- **Sempahore:** implementation of a Semaphore
- **main.cpp:** the traditional start point of the program, showing off the Mutual-Exclusion implementation

